title: Midseason All-Pro team & TNF preview
itunes:title: Midseason All-Pro team & TNF preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – break down all the latest news from around the NFL including the Patriots trading linebacker Jamie Collins to the Browns, and the retirement of Andre Johnson. Then, the heroes break down which players would make their All-Pro team based on what we’ve seen through the first half of the season, and preview the Thursday night matchup between the Buccaneers and the Falcons. Plus, Conor Orr joins us from his Haunted Mansion in New Jersey to give an update on his Power Poll.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
